ess structures obtained from\nuniform polymatroids are flat, i.e., every chain has at most 2 elements. The\nideality of some families of hierarchical access structures is proved in\nSection 5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 May 2020 20:38:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 18:40:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-26"}
