K. Finally, we also discuss the effect of anion As height on the\nelectronic structures and study possible magnetic states in these three\ncompounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 May 2020 04:49:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 08:27:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 02:32:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-04"}
